prisma_schema:
model ChatMessage {
  id              Int      @id @default(autoincrement())
  text            String
  parentMessageId String?
  createdAt       DateTime @default(now())
  chatId          Int
  History         History  @relation(fields: [chatId], references: [id])
}

model History {
  id          Int           @id @default(autoincrement())
  title       String
  createdAt   DateTime      @default(now())
  updatedAt   DateTime?
  userId      String
  User        User          @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id])
  ChatMessage ChatMessage[]
}

model Prompt {
  id        Int       @id @default(autoincrement())
  prompt    String
  title     String
  userId    String
  createdAt DateTime  @default(now())
  updatedAt DateTime?
  User      User      @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id])
}

model User {
  id        String    @id
  name      String
  avatar    String
  bio       String?
  provider  String
  createdAt DateTime  @default(now())
  History   History[]
  Prompt    Prompt[]
}
